# Git + Railway (duplicate signal)

**Same policy as `.cursor/rules/railway-deploy.mdc` (`alwaysApply: true`).**

- **Commit:** **`git add`** → **`git commit`** → **`git push`** when the user wants changes committed.
- **Deploy / redeploy:** **`git push`** **and** **`railway up --no-gitignore`** from project root when they want production updated, unless they say otherwise.

Full detail: **`railway-deploy.mdc`** and **`docs/RAILWAY_DEPLOY.md`**.
